content.text:
The database shows three charter schools in Hickman with DOC = 52. Their websites are:
1. `http://hes.hickmanschools.org`
2. `http://hcs.hickmanschools.org`
3. `http://hms.hickmanschools.org`

The claim states these websites are "all built on WordPress." The database only stores the website URLs — it does not contain any information about the technology platform (e.g., WordPress, Drupal, etc.) used to build those websites.
